<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Tomi's Kitchen</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playball&family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="icon" href="/images/logo-removebg-preview.png">
  <style>
    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }
    *, *::before, *::after {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
    }
    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      width: 100%;
      background: white;
      z-index: 1000;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 10px 30px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
    }
    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .logo img {
      height: 40px;
    }
    .logo h2 {
      font-family: 'Playball', cursive;
      color: rgb(32, 32, 59);
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 0;
    }
    nav a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: rgb(32, 32, 59);
      font-weight: bold;
      padding: 10px 15px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    nav a:hover {
      background-color: rgba(255, 183, 1, 0.376);
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .hero {
      background-image: url('/images/background%20pro.PNG');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      padding: 60px 30px;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .hero-text {
      max-width: 500px;
    }
    .hero-text h3 {
      background-color: whitesmoke;
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 5px 10px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: rgb(32, 32, 59);
    }
    .hero-text h1 {
      font-size: 50px;
      color: rgb(32, 32, 59);
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .hero-text p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: rgb(32, 32, 59);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .book-btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      background-color: rgba(255, 183, 1, 0.376);
      padding: 10px 15px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: rgb(32, 32, 59);
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .book-btn img {
      height: 20px;
      margin-right: 8px;
    }
    .hero img {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
    }
    .about {
      background-image: url('/images/background%20pro.PNG');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      padding: 50px 30px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .about img {
      width: 300px;
      height: auto;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .about h2 {
      font-size: 26px;
      color: rgb(32, 32, 59);
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .features {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 30px;
      max-width: 800px;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .feature {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .feature h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
      color: rgb(211, 151, 0);
      margin: 0;
    }
    .feature-details h3 {
      margin: 0;
      color: rgb(32, 32, 59);
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .feature-details p {
      margin: 5px 0 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: rgb(32, 32, 59);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      header {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }
      .hero {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }
      .features {
        padding: 20px;
      }
    }
    /* Footer */
    .footer {
      background-color: whitesmoke;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 1156px;
      margin: 50px auto 30px;
      padding: 1rem 1rem;
      color: rgb(32, 32, 59);
      font-weight: 500;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 7px;
      user-select: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="/images/logo-removebg-preview.png" alt="Logo">
      <h2>Tomi's Kitchen</h2>
    </div>
    <nav>
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/about">About</a>
      <a href="/contact">Contacts</a>
      <a href="/menu">Our Menus</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h3>Hi, new friend!</h3>
      <h1>We do not cook, we create your emotions!</h1>
      <p>Enjoy our delicious cuisines</p>
      <a href="/book" class="book-btn">
        <img src="/images/menu-removebg-preview.png" alt="Menu Icon"> Book A Table
      </a>
    </div>
    <img src="/images/food_project-removebg-preview.png" alt="Delicious Food">
  </section>

  <section class="about">
    <img src="/images/back11.PNG" alt="About Image">
    <h2>We are doing more than you expect</h2>

    <div class="features">
      <div class="feature">
        <h1>01</h1>
        <div class="feature-details">
          <h3>We are located in the city center</h3>
          <p>This makes it much easier for you to locate us, reducing stress.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <h1>02</h1>
        <div class="feature-details">
          <h3>Fresh, organic ingredients</h3>
          <p>We care about your health and use fresh, organic ingredients to boost your immune system.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <h1>03</h1>
        <div class="feature-details">
          <h3>Own Fast Delivery</h3>
          <p>We deliver faster than expected â€“ that's how much we value our customers.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
<footer class="footer">
     &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Tomi's Kitchen. All rights reserved. 
</footer>
</body>
</html>
